OL,3,CICRIR requests to Gardai for Troubles
OL,4,Cmurders information turned down
OL,6,FThe Independent Commission for
OL,7,FReconciliation and Information
OL,8,FRecovery (ICRIR) has said that all
OL,9,Frequests it has made to An Garda
OL,10,FSiochana for information on Troubles
OL,11,Fmurders have been turned down.
OL,13,FICRIR Commissioner for Investigations
OL,14,FPeter Sheridan and chief Sir Declan
OL,15,FMorgan were giving evidence to the
OL,16,FStormont Executive Office scrutiny
OL,17,Fcommittee on Wednesday.
OL,26,@kD@XrtrD@BrtrD@Frp
