PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781768877
OL,3,CICRIR requests to Gardai for Troubles
OL,4,Cmurders information turned down
OL,6,FIt was revealed that during a meeting
OL,7,Fin January with the Garda Commissioner
OL,8,FJustin Kelly, they were told that the
OL,9,FIrish government is not permitting the
OL,10,Fdisclosure of information until the UK
OL,11,FGovernment passes the legacy
OL,12,Flegislation currently making its way
OL,13,Fthrough parliament.
OL,15,FSir Declan said they needed more
OL,16,Fpowers and also co-operation from the
OL,17,FRepublic of Ireland to tackle their
OL,18,F123 case load, which included some of
OL,19,Fthe most infamous bombings in the
OL,20,Fhistory of Northern Ireland.
OL,26,@kD@Xrt
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/4
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
