PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781768877
OL,3,CICRIR requests to Gardai for Troubles
OL,4,Cmurders information turned down
OL,6,FThe committee also heard the ICRIR
OL,7,Fwill have to consider all options if
OL,8,Fit does not get the funding it needs
OL,9,Fto carry out its work.
OL,11,FSir Declan said the organisation was
OL,12,Fin talks with the Treasury.
OL,14,FMr Sheridan said the organisation was
OL,15,Frunning at less than 50% of the
OL,16,Fresources it needed.
OL,18,FThe ICRIR was set up by the previous
OL,19,Fgovernment's Legacy Act after inquests
OL,20,Finto Troubles deaths were halted.
OL,26,@kD@Xrt
